    {
      "content": "Overview",
      "pos": [
        975,
        983
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Search can integrate directly with some common data sources, removing the need to write code to index your data.",
      "pos": [
        985,
        1103
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To set up this up, you can call the Azure Search API to create and manage <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>indexers<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> and <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>data sources<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        1104,
        1212
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1215,
        1438
      ],
      "content": "A <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>data source<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> specifies what data needs to be indexed, credentials to access the data, and hints to enable Azure Search to efficiently identify changes in the data (such as modified or deleted rows in a database table)."
    },
    {
      "content": "An <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>indexer<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> describes how the data flows from your data source into a search index.",
      "pos": [
        1440,
        1526
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "An indexer can:",
      "pos": [
        1527,
        1542
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Perform a one-time copy of the data",
      "pos": [
        1547,
        1582
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Sync Azure Search index with changes in the data source on a schedule",
      "pos": [
        1585,
        1654
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Be invoked on-demand at any time to perform the copy",
      "pos": [
        1657,
        1709
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The following data sources are currently supported:",
      "pos": [
        1711,
        1762
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure SQL Database",
      "pos": [
        1766,
        1784
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "DocumentDB",
      "pos": [
        1787,
        1797
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "We're considering adding support for additional data sources in the future.",
      "pos": [
        1800,
        1875
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To help us prioritize these decisions, please provide your feedback on the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure Search feedback forum<ept id=\"p1\">](http://feedback.azure.com/forums/263029-azure-search)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        1876,
        2035
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        2037,
        2149
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>NOTE<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> The features described here are supported beginning with Azure Search API version <ph id=\"ph1\">`2014-10-20-Preview`</ph>."
