      "pos": [
        5535,
        5558
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The body of the request contains a data source definition, which includes type of the data source, credentials to read the data, as well as an optional data change detection and data deletion detection policies that are used to efficiently identify changed or deleted data in the data source when used with a periodically scheduled indexer.",
      "pos": [
        5560,
        5900
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The syntax for structuring the request payload is as follows.",
      "pos": [
        5904,
        5965
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "A sample request is provided further on in this topic.",
      "pos": [
