      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "A data source name must only contain lowercase letters, digits or dashes, cannot start or end with dashes and is limited to 128 characters.",
      "pos": [
        6714,
        6853
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        6856,
        6895
      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">`description`</ph>: An optional description."
    },
    {
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">`type`</ph>: Required.",
      "pos": [
        6899,
        6916
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use <ph id=\"ph1\">`azuresql`</ph> for an Azure SQL data source, <ph id=\"ph2\">`docdb`</ph> for a  DocumentDB data source.",
      "pos": [
        6917,
        7000
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7003,
        7015
      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">`container`</ph>:"
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7023,
        7172
      ],
      "content": "The required <ph id=\"ph1\">`name`</ph> property specifies the table or view (for Azure SQL data source) or collection (for DocumentDB data source) that will be indexed."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7180,
        7376
      ],
      "content": "DocumentDB data sources also support an optional <ph id=\"ph1\">`query`</ph> property that allows you to specify a query that flattens an arbitrary JSON document layout into a flat schema that Azure Search can index."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7382,
        7477
      ],
      "content": "The optional <ph id=\"ph1\">`dataChangeDetectionPolicy`</ph> and <ph id=\"ph2\">`dataDeletionDetectionPolicy`</ph> are described below."
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Data Change Detection Policies<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>",
      "pos": [
        7522,
        7556
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The purpose of a data change detection policy is to efficiently identify changed data items.",
      "pos": [
        7558,
